class Character(*args, **kwargs):
    request by default: species, gender, system, 
    /Species, /Gender
    -> Name
    --> List, generator? default names=gen, but can be names="x/"
    -> Age
    Appearance
    Quirks
    /System?:
    /-> NPC Type?
    --> Characteristics
        dnd: [randint(1,6) for i in range(4)]; list.remove(min(list))
        gsys>minion: shuffle([1, 1, 1, 2, 2, 2])
        gsys>rival: shuffle([1, 2, 2, 2, 3, 3])
        gsys>nemesis: shuffle([2, 2, 3, 3, 3, 3])
    /--> Skills
    --> Items
    if NPC:
    --> Profession
    --> Low HP
    --> Levels, if any
    if PC:
    --> Class
    --> Proper stats

